resources.description: With the deepening reform of higher education, the profession of being college secretary has also been standardized and improved. College secretary must formulate proper occupational career plan according to his or her own characteristcs, realize the significance and necessity of career planning, and pay attention to career orientation and initiative taking, clear stage target so as to construct a reasonable knowledge structure, develop professional capabilities, and to obtain a better and extended career.
resources.name: On the Occupational Career Planning for College Secretary
